Point shapes available in R

Show point shapes available in R.

show_point_shapes()

Value

a ggplot.

See also

ggpar and ggline.

Examples

show_point_shapes()+
 theme_minimal()
#> Scale for 'y' is already present. Adding another scale for 'y', which will
#> replace the existing scale.
